title: Dean Parkway- Top Floor Studio Apartment for September 1
posting_body: ['Studio  Apartment - Dean Parkway/Lakes area - Minneapolis', '2905 East Dean Parkway, Apt. 305  Minneapolis,  MN   55416', 'To schedule a showing of this apartment contact the building caretaker, Kevin, at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Photos are not from this apartment but are from a similar apartment in the building.', '$950.00/month', 'Utilities included in Rent: heat, trash removal, gas for the range.', ' Residents pay electricity, water/sewer and cable/internet if wanted.', 'KEY FEATURES:', '-Year Built:  1925', '-Square', 'Footage:  432', '-Bedrooms:  Studio', '-Bathrooms:  1 Bath', '-Hardwood Floors', '-Parking:  outdoor reserved lot at $80/month or reserved heated garage parking for $130.00/mo.', ' Inquire about     availability', '-Lease', 'Duration:  1 Year.', '6 and 9 month lease options available at an additional charge', '-Deposit:  $500', '-Pets Policy:  No Pets', '-Laundry:  Shared', '-Floor:', 'Third floor', 'To schedule a showing of this apartment or for more information please phone the building caretaker, Kevin, at', 'show contact info', '.', 'A Hornig Companies community   -   Apply on-line at <URL>', "Calhoun Beach Apartments keeps the essence of the 1920's alive in a beautiful park-like setting a half block from Bde Maka Ska.  Built in 1925, the building is a true classic, with details like silk wallcoverings that reflect the great design and elegance of the era.", ' The apartments have the original oak hardwood flooring along with large windows, arches, wide trim and other classic details.', ' More recent enhancements to the property include a patio with BBQ and a heated garage with reserved parking available.', ' Located on Dean Parkway behind the Calhoun Beach club, you will love living just steps from Lake Bde Maka Ska and the Midtown Greenway entrance.', ' Whole Foods, Lake of the Isles and Uptown are just blocks away.']
